<lb n="6"/><hi rend="grantha">de</hi>va<hi rend="grantha">rā</hi>ya<hi rend="grantha">ma hārā</hi> yar tiruvaṇṇāmalai tāṉikarkku nirupam <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied><note n="72-1">The language of this record from here is Kannaḍa.</note>tuḷuvar ceṉapokanayiṉāṉmele nimma <hi rend="grantha">stā</hi>na<hi rend="grantha">dha</hi> vairākikaḷu
